27:16.780 --> 27:18.460
 and our waking states is divided

27:18.460 --> 27:21.520
 into these 90 minute cycles or so-called ultradian cycles.

27:21.520 --> 27:24.200
 So what I like to do is set a timer for 90 minutes.

27:24.200 --> 27:26.200
