29:35.360 --> 29:38.440
 Try and give yourself some time to deliberately decompress,

29:38.440 --> 29:41.200
 to let your mental states idle,

29:41.200 --> 29:43.040
 to not be focused on any one thing.

29:43.040 --> 29:46.020
